room_title: Escape room "Crime Scene" by Murder Escape in Tulsa
review: My friends and I had a great time in this escape room!  Perfect for the spooky season!

room_title: Escape room "Crime Scene" by Murder Escape in Tulsa
review: This room was very clever! My only reason for not giving a "best" rating was because of the low light level and having to crouch down for a couple of the puzzle/locks. It is definitely not for those of us with "old bones". Otherwise, it was great!
